                    <p class="text-slate-600 text-lg">The data is irrefutable: the single best decision is to start investing early (Age 20 is ideal). Holding cash is a guaranteed path to wealth erosion, as seen in the "Under the Mattress" chart where value is decimated. Your primary financial goal must be to ensure your Real Return on investments significantly exceeds the inflation rate.</p>
